-the-art performance on three widely used datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2018 15:12:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Jan 2018 06:22:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
