otometry. These results\nfurther strengthen the evidence that the family of very hot gas giant\nexoplanets commonly exhibit thermal inversions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2018 15:20:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Feb 2018 11:30:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Apr 2018 16:04:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-26"}
